<body>
	
<header>
	Read these sentences from letters and decide if the language is formal or informal.
</header>
	
<section id="body">
  <img class="rightFloat" src="../media/SS_GW_005.jpg" mode="1" id="1001"/>
  <br/>
  <ol id="questionList">
    <br/>
    <li id="q1">The first thing I'd do if I were you is go and see his teacher.<a id="a1">Formal</a><tab/><a id="a2">Informal</a><br/></li>
    <br/>
    <li id="q2">I would like to know whether it would be possible for transportation to be arranged.<a id="a3">Formal</a><tab/><a id="a4">Informal</a><br/></li>
    <br/>
    <li id="q3">My family doctor informed the Central Hospital immediately following the diagnosis and explained the seriousness of my condition.<a id="a5">Formal</a><tab/><a id="a6">Informal</a><br/></li>
    <br/>
    <li id="q4">I have considerable experience in the field of animal care.<a id="a7">Formal</a><tab/><a id="a8">Informal</a><br/></li>
    <br/>
    <li id="q5">It's a really good read.<a id="a9">Formal</a><tab/><a id="a10">Informal</a><br/></li>
    <br/>
    <li id="q6">Our children are unable to walk home from school unless they are accompanied by an adult.<a id="a11">Formal</a><tab/><a id="a12">Informal</a><br/></li>
    <br/>
    <li id="q7">You really should check out the job ads on the Internet too.<a id="a13">Formal</a><tab/><a id="a14">Informal</a><br/></li>
    <br/>
    <li id="q8">We were particularly impressed by the number of ramps for wheelchair users.<a id="a15">Formal</a><tab/><a id="a16">Informal</a><br/></li>
    <br/>
    <li id="q9">I have suffered from acute sleep deprivation for a number of years.<a id="a17">Formal</a><tab/><a id="a18">Informal</a><br/></li>
    <br/>
    <li id="q10">I strongly feel that there is an unacceptable level of violence in the programme and that, therefore, the series should be broadcast at a more appropriate time.<a id="a19">Formal</a><tab/><a id="a20">Informal</a><br/></li>
    <br/>
    <li id="q11">I really can't stand football.<a id="a21">Formal</a><tab/><a id="a22">Informal</a><br/></li>
    <br/>
    <li id="q12">The officers on duty responded to our call within a matter of minutes.<a id="a23">Formal</a><tab/><a id="a24">Informal</a><br/></li>
